data.details:
FSCJ Artist Series presents The Tony Award-Winning Production - ANNIE at the Times-Union Center, Moran Theater from October 21-26, 2014.

A Special Scout Discount, including an ANNIE Girl Scout patch and post-show chat back with the cast, is available for the Wednesday, October 22 performance at 7:30 PM. Scout tickets are $27.50* in B section seating (FULL: $67.50) and $22.50* in C section seating (FULL: $57.50).

For tickets, contact Cindy de Padua or Meredith Ramey at (904) 442-2947 or groupsales@fscj.edu.

Visit www.artseriesjax.org NEW website to learn more about the FSCJ Artist Series 2014-2015 Broadway Season Line-up. *Price is all-inclusive.

Scout discount not valid on previously purchased tickets, facility usage fee and service charge not discounted. Offer subject to availability and may be withdrawn at any time.
